      <event start="T1616-799" end="T1618-335">mi to ful ne ustreza. </event>
      <event start="T1618-335" end="T1621-295">Pač mene vročina ubija in </event>
      <event start="T1621-295" end="T1622-953">da sem, </event>
      <event start="T1622-953" end="T474">da sem torej zunaj ... pa to, </event>
      <event start="T474" end="T475">mi je, </event>
